2. âœ… Make screensaver scripts executable
   â€¢ ~/.config/hypr/scripts/screensaver
   â€¢ ~/.config/hypr/scripts/screensaver-launch

3. âœ… Add screensaver listener to hypridle.conf
   â€¢ Triggers after 150 seconds (2.5 minutes) of inactivity
   â€¢ Only if screen is NOT locked
   â€¢ Non-invasive (adds new listener, doesn't modify existing ones)

4. âœ… Add window rules to WindowRules.conf
   â€¢ Makes screensaver fullscreen
   â€¢ Proper window class matching
   â€¢ No conflicts with other apps

5. âœ… Create backup files
   â€¢ hypridle.conf.backup.*
   â€¢ WindowRules.conf.backup.*
   â€¢ Easy to revert if needed


